➜乒坛盛会见证“河南力量”
http://www.sohu.com/a/433869327_162758	3601
<p><img src="//p8.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201124/bd5b866cf2d347a19a9f9112f7510d54.jpeg" /></p>
